Keuka Park has the highest ratio of women to men in the state of New York, due to the university.  As of the 2010 census, there were 755 females (66.4%) to 382 males (33.6%).  The median age was 21.3 years.<ref name="U.S. Census Bureau">{{cite web|title=Profile of General Population and Housing Characteristics: 2010 – Keuka Park CDP, NY|url=https://factfinder.census.gov/bkmk/table/1.0/en/DEC/10_DP/DPDP1/1600000US3639463|access-date=2019-06-05|archive-url=https://archive.today/20200213094242/https://factfinder.census.gov/bkmk/table/1.0/en/DEC/10_DP/DPDP1/1600000US3639463|archive-date=2020-02-13|url-status=dead}}</ref>

